dininginfo.name: Sixty-Four North
dininginfo.description: Welcome to Sixty-Four North! test We hope you enjoy our mix of California cuisine featuring local vegetables and trending international dishes. Reservations are strongly encouraged; please call 858.822.6899.

nutrition.disclaimer: Please be aware that UCSD Housing Dining Hospitality Services handles and prepares egg, milk, wheat, shellfish, fish, soy, peanut, tree nut products, and other potential allergens in our restaurants and kitchens. We are in the process of verifying our nutrition information and allergens. Should you have any questions, please contact our nutrition team at HDHdiningmenus@ucsd.edu.
